  building with libjpeg.so.62 API wrt #479848 by Martin von Gagern

  31 May 2013; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org>
  files/xawtv-3.95-pagemask-fix.patch:
  Fix relative paths in patch (bug #471818 by Aaron Pelton).

