*xawtv-3.95 (13 Jan 2006)

  13 Jan 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  +files/tv-fonts-1.1-nox.patch, +files/xawtv-3.95-autocolor.patch,
  +files/xawtv-3.95-bindnow.patch, +files/xawtv-3.95-sparc.patch,
  +xawtv-3.95.ebuild:
